"""Test for get_element_dict."""
component_dict = self.utils.get_masking_view_component_dict(self.data.smis_mv_4
    )
element_dict = self.utils.get_element_dict(component_dict, '-CD', '', self.
    data.m_portgroup, self.data.m_host_name)
self.assertEqual('myhost', element_dict['initiator_group'])
self.assertEqual('myportgroup', element_dict['port_group'])
self.assertEqual('OS-myhost-SRP_1-SilverNONE-myportgroup-CD', element_dict[
    'new_sg_name'])
self.assertEqual('OS-myhost-I-myportgroup-MV', element_dict['new_mv_name'])
self.assertEqual('Silver', element_dict['service_level'])
